eroes as the chosen wielder of the Mana Sword and their two companions on the journey to claim the holy blade and preserve what remains of mana power.\n\nThe power of Mana drains rapidly from the land and the Mana Tree begins to wither\u2026", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 38, "name": "Open world"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/trials-of-mana--1", "videos": [{"id": 113581, "name": "JP TV Commercial", "video_id": "NGmlo8Pw8x0", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NGmlo8Pw8x0", "title": "CM\u3000\u30b9\u30af\u30a6\u30a7\u30a2\u3000\u8056\u5263\u4f1d\u8aac3\u3000\uff08SFC\uff09", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NGmlo8Pw8x0/hqdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 113582, "name": "Gameplay Video", "video_id": "nZ9nuZeD4xY", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZ9nuZeD4xY", "title": "Seiken Densetsu 3 Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/nZ9nuZeD4xY/hqdefault.jpg"}], "collections": [{"id": 1920, "name": "Mana"}]}